Package com.pb.sawdust.util.sql.wrappers

Provides wrappers for JDBC classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WrappedConnection
    The WrappedConnection class provides a wrapper class for java.sql.Connection implementations which can be used as a convenience to selectively override one or more of Connection's methods.
    WrappedResultSet
    The ResultSetWrapper class provides a wrapper class for java.sql.ResultSet implementations which can be used as a convenience to selectively override one or more of ResultSet's methods.

Package com.pb.sawdust.util.sql.wrappers Description

Provides wrappers for JDBC classes. These are convenient when extensions of provided classes are needed, but the implementations of the classes are not known or available (or, in a generic sense, needed) at compile time.
